features.additionalInfo: A guaranteed rate for a selected period between 1 - 60 months

If you want to withdraw your Term Deposit before it matures you'll need to give us 31 days' notice. A reduced rate of interest will apply in these circumstances. For full details refer to our Terms and Conditions
We'll send you a written renewal notice before your deposit matures.
For deposits of $500,000 and over, rates are by negotiation.

fees.name: CASH_DEPOSIT_FEE
fees.additionalInfo: Payable when you deposit cash over the counter at an Auswide Bank branch/agency

fees.name: INTERNAL_TRANSFER_FEE_-
fees.additionalInfo: Payable for any transfer between two Auswide Bank accounts at an Auswide Bank branch/agency

fees.name: CHEQUE_DEPOSIT_PROCESSING_FEE
fees.additionalInfo: Payable per cheque deposited at an Auswide Bank branch or by mail

fees.name: BPAY_FEE_-_ELECTRONIC
fees.additionalInfo: Payable when you make an electronic BPAY payment

fees.name: DIRECT_DEBIT_FEE_-_ELECTRONIC
fees.additionalInfo: Payable if we process a direct debit to your account (including payments you initiate electronically)

fees.name: EXTERNAL_PAYMENT_FEE_-_ELECTRONIC
fees.additionalInfo: Payable if you request us to process an electronic payment to an account at another Australian Bank or financial institution

fees.name: RTGS_OUTWARD_PAYMENT_FEE
fees.additionalInfo: Payable each time you request a high value, time critical payment from your account to another financial institution on a real time basis for    same day    payment

fees.name: TELEGPRAPHIC_TRANSFER_FEE
fees.additionalInfo: payable each time you request an electronic transmission of funds to an account at an overseas bank. $AU cuurency $50 per transfer OR foreign currency $30 per transfer

fees.name: BPAY_FEE_-_INTERNET_AND_MOBILE_BANKING
fees.additionalInfo: Payable when you make a BPAY payment through internet or mobile banking

fees.name: EXTERNAL_PAYMENT_FEE_-_INTERNET_AND_MOBILE_BANKING
fees.additionalInfo: Payable if you request us to process an electronic payment to another Australian bank or financial institution

fees.name: BPAY_FEE_-_PHONE_BANKING
fees.additionalInfo: Payable when you make a BPAY payment through phone banking

fees.name: PAPER_STATEMENT_FEE
fees.additionalInfo: Payable when we issue you with your statement of account in paper

fees.name: ADDITIONAL_STATEMENT_FEE
fees.additionalInfo: Payable when you request us to issue you an additional statement of account

fees.name: E-STATEMENT_FEE
fees.additionalInfo: Payable when we issue you with an electronic statement of account

fees.name: NON-RESIDENT_WITHHOLDING_TAX
fees.additionalInfo: Levied on accounts held by a non resident of Australia and where an Australian Tax File Number had not been quoted to us
